# Copy this file to .env and fill in your key
# The pipeline uses this for:
#   - LLM-based spoof generation (--use-llm flag in generate_attacks.py)
#   - LLM judge evaluation (evaluate_llm.py)
# Without a key the pipeline still runs fully — using rule-based generation
# and skipping the LLM judge stage.
# OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here